{
  "text": "While existing literature considers the role of AI in writing as continuously generating possible ideas with engaging questions (Dale & Viethen, 2021; Rowland, 2023), students in this envision role of GenAI as a thought facilitator, facilitating various thinking processes during writing tasks, rather than merely providing information or guidance.",
